cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DS

The paper deals with recommender systems, which are commonly studied in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of side information and collaborative learning also suggests a potential fit for Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories. Finally, the use of data and the evaluation of the proposed algorithm aligns with the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category.
